Israeli police enter the Red Cross compound and arrest two more Palestinian MPs associated with Hamas. (CNN)Dharun Ravi, the U.S. student who secretly filmed the sexual activities of his gay room-mate Tyler Clementi, who later committed suicide when the film was exposed, is sentenced to 30 days in prison by a New Jersey judge. Ravi avoids the maximum sentence of 10 years' imprisonment. (BBC) (Al Jazeera)